Tabnine AI Complete Review 2026

Privacy-Focused AI Code Assistant

What is Tabnine?

Tabnine is an AI code assistant that prioritizes privacy and allows your code to remain on your machine. It offers AI-powered code completion with optional local models.

Key Features

  • Privacy-First: Code never leaves your environment
  • Local AI: Run models entirely on your machine
  • Team Training: Custom models trained on your codebase
  • Multi-Language: Supports all major languages
  • Enterprise Ready: SOC 2 compliant, self-hosted options
